“As a bank, we understand that the commercial opportunities available to our agribusiness customers are heavily dependent on the quality of their natural capital assets. … [T]hose who manage their natural capital well – their soil health, water, energy and bio-diversity – tend to be more resilient and more productive over time. …We need to manage our natural capital with the same diligence that we manage our financial capital.” (
Henry, 2016
).
